    <name>CUE 02 Doe Ridge</name>
    <desc>Follow Doe Ridge. First official segment here: Doe Ridge 1. Either direction allowed; follow map arrows. This is a navigation cue, not the full segment-credit audit.</desc>
  </wpt>
